'''Ferḥat Mhenni''', d aselway n Amusu [[Timanit n Tmurt n Iqbayliyen (MAK)]], ilul-d deg 05 n Meɣres 1951 deg taddart n Illula, deg tama n temdinin n [[Buzegan]], [[Iɛezzugen]], akk-d 
[[Aqbu]]. 


Asmi i d-kemmel almad-ines deg Tesdawit n Lezzayer (tamaneɣt) yebda-d tikli-ines di ccna deg 1973 imi yewwi tarrazt tamezwarut n tafaska tatrart n ccna n Lezzayer. 
Kra n lweqt mbeɛd isbeggen-d iman-is belli yella mgal anabad n iɣil n Lezzayer imi yebda-d abrid n tigwin; ɣef igiten agi yekcem-d ɣef lḥebs 13 iberdan.

Mbeɛd [[Tafsut Taberkant]], imi Tamselta n Lezzayer tenɣa yiwen weqcic amelsi yettusemman [[Masinisa Germaḥ]], Ferhat Mhenni isbed ''Amussu i Timanit n Tmurt''; tuddsa ixeddmen akken a tessiwed ar timanit n tmurt n leqbayel. Llan wid i qqaren belli ɣef demma n wannecta i yettwanɣa mmi-s Ameẓian Mhenni deg 2004.


'''Amussu i Timanit n Tmurt''' (''MAK''), [[Agraw n Yedles d Tugdut]] (''RCD''), akk-d [[Tirni Iɣallen Inemlayen]] (''FFS'') d ikabaren isertiyen i sɛan ccan deg Tmurt n Izwawen.

